      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## View Doctrine\n\nInside a task graph, there is no separate `task-summary` concept for new work. The graph exposes two derived surfaces:\n\n- `summary`: the outward summary view. Use it for readable document-style summary data.\n- `task`: the rolled-up task view. Use it for goal, status, and the task-shaped body.\n\nKeep existing `task-summary` nodes only for legacy graphs and migrate consumers toward explicit `summary` and `task` views.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
